{"title":"DesignPattern","date":"2020-06-20T05:26:01.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jun 20, 2020","L":"06/20/2020","MM-DD":"06-20"},"link":"2020/06/20/designPattern(class)","tags":["JS","designPattern"],"updated":"2020-06-20T06:46:45.189Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><h1 id=\"DesignPattern\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/06/20/designPattern(class)#DesignPattern\"></a>DesignPattern</h1>\n<h2 id=\"DesignPattern-是什麼？？\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/06/20/designPattern(class)#DesignPattern-是什麼？？\"></a>DesignPattern 是什麼？？</h2>\n<p>在軟體工程中，<font color=\"red\">設計模式（design pattern）</font>是對軟體設計中普遍存在（反覆出現）的各種問題，所提出的<mark>解決方案</mark>。</p>\n<p>這個術語是由埃里希·伽瑪（Erich Gamma）等人在1990年代從建築設計領域引入到計算機科學的。</p>\n<p>設計模式並不直接用來完成程式碼的編寫，而是<font color=\"blue\"><em><strong>描述在各種不同情況下，要怎麼解決問題的一種方案</strong></em>。</font></p>\n<p>設計模式能使不穩定依賴於相對穩定、具體依賴於相對抽象，避免會引起麻煩的緊耦合，以增強軟體設計面對並適應變化的能力。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Class-的建立\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/06/20/designPattern(class)#Class-的建立\"></a>Class 的建立</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CTP8AIo.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<div class=\"danger\">\n<p>在JS中，我會把<strong>class</strong>想成是一份蓋房子的<strong>設計搞</strong>，一個可參考的文件，沒有 實體 (Instance) 的概念，屬<strong>靜態</strong>的。</p>\n<p><strong>object</strong>是一個根據設計搞所建立的房子，看的到、摸的到的實體，屬於<strong>動態</strong>的，狀態會隨時改變，但架構與行為不會改變。</p>\n</div>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 創立class</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">People</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// constructor 用來引入靜態資源</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(name, age) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.name = name;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.age = age;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    eat() {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">`<span class=\"subst\">${<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.name}</span> 吃東西`</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    speak() {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">`我的名字是<span class=\"subst\">${<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.name}</span>,我的年紀是<span class=\"subst\">${<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.age}</span>`</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">}<span class=\"comment\">//class</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"￼1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/06/20/designPattern(class)#￼1\"></a><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// object 的建立</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> yachen = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> People(<span class=\"string\">'jack'</span>, <span class=\"number\">30</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">jack.eat();</span><br><span class=\"line\">jack.speak();</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> xxxtim = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> People(<span class=\"string\">'xxxtim'</span>, <span class=\"number\">27</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">xxxtim.eat();</span><br><span class=\"line\">xxxtim.speak();</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure></h2>\n<h2 id=\"class的繼承\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/06/20/designPattern(class)#class的繼承\"></a>class的繼承</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/z5tkQSX.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<div class=\"danger\">\n<p>父類別如爸爸，子類別如兒子，爸爸有的，兒子一旦繼承了也會有，爸爸有的你不但擁有，還可以加上兒子自己的東西。好處是可以<strong>減少重覆撰寫相同的程式碼</strong></p>\n</div>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 建立一個父類</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">People</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// constructor 用來引入靜態資源</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(name, age) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.name = name;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.age = age;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    eat() {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">`<span class=\"subst\">${<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.name}</span> 吃東西`</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    speak() {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">`我的名字是<span class=\"subst\">${<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.name}</span>,我的年紀是<span class=\"subst\">${<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.age}</span>`</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">}<span class=\"comment\">//class</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 子類繼承父類</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Student</span> <span class=\"keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"title\">People</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(name, age, number) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// super:表示把參數傳給父類的構造函數執行</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">super</span>(name, age);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.number = number;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    study() {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        comsole.log(<span class=\"string\">`<span class=\"subst\">${<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.name}</span>study`</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"￼4\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/06/20/designPattern(class)#￼4\"></a><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 建立 object</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> titan = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Student(<span class=\"string\">'titan'</span>, <span class=\"number\">17</span>, <span class=\"string\">'A123'</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">titan.study();</span><br><span class=\"line\">titan.eat();</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure></h2>\n<h2 id=\"題目練習\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/06/20/designPattern(class)#題目練習\"></a>題目練習</h2>\n<div class=\"danger\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XPfA3Oi.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>叫車時，可以叫快車或漫車，任何車都有車牌和名稱</li>\n<li>快車每公里1元/慢車每公里2元</li>\n<li>車輛行使時，顯示車輛資訊</li>\n<li>到達目的時，顯示金額</li>\n<li>Q:如果叫快車，行駛5KM，共需多少錢？</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Car</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(name, plate) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.name = name;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.plate = plate;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">FastCar</span> <span class=\"keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"title\">Car</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(name, plate) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">super</span>(name, plate);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.price = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">SlowCar</span> <span class=\"keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"title\">Car</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(name, plate) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">super</span>(name, plate);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.price = <span class=\"number\">2</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">};</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Trip</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(car, distance) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.car = car;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.distance = distance;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    };</span><br><span class=\"line\">    star() {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">`開始發車，車子名稱：<span class=\"subst\">${<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.car.name}</span>/車牌名稱:<span class=\"subst\">${<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.car.plate}</span>`</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    };</span><br><span class=\"line\">    end() {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">`到達目的，價格：<span class=\"subst\">${<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.car.price * <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.distance}</span>`</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> car = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> FastCar(<span class=\"string\">'BMW'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'xq-9121'</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> trip = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Trip(car, <span class=\"number\">10</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">trip.star();</span><br><span class=\"line\">trip.end();</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DSvZDvv.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>資料來源：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://sites.google.com/a/mis.nsysu.edu.tw/cheng-shi-zi-xun-wang/java-jin-jie-pian/wu-jian-dao-xiang/2-shen-me-shi-ji-cheng\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://sites.google.com/a/mis.nsysu.edu.tw/cheng-shi-zi-xun-wang/java-jin-jie-pian/wu-jian-dao-xiang/2-shen-me-shi-ji-cheng</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/super\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/super</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%9D%A2%E5%90%91%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/面向对象程序设计</a></li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>","next":{"title":"[測試]Jest install","link":"2020/06/17/jestInstall"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/06/20/designPattern(class)/","toc":[{"title":"","id":"DesignPattern","index":"1","children":[{"title":"","id":"DesignPattern-是什麼？？","index":"1.1"},{"title":"","id":"Class-的建立","index":"1.2"},{"title":"","id":"￼1","index":"1.3"},{"title":"","id":"class的繼承","index":"1.4"},{"title":"","id":"￼4","index":"1.5"},{"title":"","id":"題目練習","index":"1.6"}]}]}